- âœ… **Faculty Dashboard** (session management & QR code generator)  
- âœ… **Admin Panel** (manage students, faculty, departments, subjects)  
- âœ… **Analytics Dashboard** (attendance trends, low attendance list)  
- âœ… **AI Insights (GPT API)** (predict shortages, suggest actions)  
- âœ… **Email Notifications** (auto-send alerts for <75% attendance)  
- âœ… **Chatbot Assistant** (natural language queries like *â€œMy attendance in Physics?â€*)  
- âœ… **Responsive UI** (TailwindCSS + Alpine.js + Chart.js)  

